fulltitle: The CIA, Money Laundering, and Organized Crime w/ Economist Michael Hudson
title: The CIA, Money Laundering, and Organized Crime w/ Economist Michael Hudson
_filename: _The CIA, Money Laundering, and Organized Crime w_ Economist Michael Hudson.webm
description:
Full interview: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hH9pzzIIEj4
Credit: Global University for Sustainability

#CIA #Drugs #Economics 

Economist Michael Hudson discusses his time working as an economist at Chase Manhattan Bank. He was approached by an officer of the Central Intelligence Agency who enlisted him to study the economy of organized crime. The CIA wanted to study using laundered drug money (among other lucrative criminal activity) to independently fund Agency operations.
